name: Cargo Rush (CemKaanU)
description:
Hey!

Because of the heavy snowfall, you are stuck in the warehouse as the last cargo agent.

As you are stuck indoors trying to stay cozy, you might as well sort some cargo.

Make yourself a cup of coffee and sort cargo at your own pace. But most importantly, don't forget to stay cozy!
